snippet.title: Atari 50: The Wider World of Atari - Full DLC Tour (Steam)
snippet.description:
This tour showcases all the games featured on The Wider World of Atari DLC expansion for Atari 50. 

Chapters:
00:00 - Intro
00:20 - Atari Video Cube [2600]
06:27 - Avalanche [Arcade]
08:20 - Avalanche [Atari 800]
10:13 - Berzerk [Arcade]
12:25 - Berzerk [2600]
14:39 - Berzerk [5200]
17:10 - Berzerk: Voice Enhanced [2600]
18:50 - Desert Falcon [2600]
21:09 - Destroyer [Arcade]
[SKIPPED] - Football [2P only]
25:57 - Frenzy [Arcade]
27:30 - Off the Wall [2600]
30:33 - Red Baron [Arcade]
32:57 - Sky Diver [2600]
34:43 - Skydiver [Arcade]
36:33 - Steeplechase [2600]
38:13 - Stellar Track [2600]
40:26 - Submarine Commander [2600]
43:30 - Super Bug [Arcade]

Atari 50: The Anniversary Celebration and all the games listed (C) Atari
Developed by Digital Eclipse
Also released for Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Nintendo Switch and Atari VCS
